    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Physical works, such as drawings and written documents, that were used in the planning or execution of a definable physical work or set of works; also includes the finished works. Alternatively, a project may be planned, but unexecuted. For the conceptual activities of planning or carrying out of proposed undertakings or creations, use projects (artistic concepts).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
